{"word":"G3140 - μαρτυρέω - martyréō - mar-too-reh'-o - Charge","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μαρτυρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>martyréō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>mar-too-reh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Charge"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சாட்சிகளாயிரு, சாட்சிகொடு, சாட்சிசொல், சாட்சியாக அறிவி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be a witness, to bear witness, testify"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3144 - μάρτυς - mártys - mar'-toos/3144\">G3144</a>; to <i>be a witness</i>, that is, <i>testify</i> (literally or figuratively): - charge, give [evidence], bear record, have (obtain, of) good (honest) report, be well reported of, testify, give (have) testimony, (be, bear, give, obtain) witness."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1263 - διαμαρτύρομαι - diamartýromai - dee-am-ar-too'-rom-ahee/1263\">G1263</a>, <a href=\"#/G1957 - ἐπιμαρτυρέω - epimartyréō - ep-ee-mar-too-reh'-o/1957\">G1957</a>, <a href=\"#/G2649 - καταμαρτυρέω - katamartyréō - kat-am-ar-too-reh'-o/2649\">G2649</a>, <a href=\"#/G3140 - μαρτυρέω - martyréō - mar-too-reh'-o/3140\">G3140</a>, <a href=\"#/G3141 - μαρτυρία - martyría - mar-too-ree'-ah/3141\">G3141</a>, <a href=\"#/G3142 - μαρτύριον - martýrion - mar-too'-ree-on/3142\">G3142</a>, <a href=\"#/G3143 - μαρτύρομαι - martýromai - mar-too'-rom-ahee/3143\">G3143</a>, <a href=\"#/G3144 - μάρτυς - mártys - mar'-toos/3144\">G3144</a>, <a href=\"#/G4303 - προμαρτύρομαι - promartýromai - prom-ar-too'-rom-ahee/4303\">G4303</a>, <a href=\"#/G4828 - συμμαρτυρέω - symmartyréō - soom-mar-too-reh'-o/4828\">G4828</a>, <a href=\"#/G4901 - συνεπιμαρτυρέω - synepimartyréō - soon-ep-ee-mar-too-reh'-o/4901\">G4901</a>, <a href=\"#/G5575 - ψευδομάρτυρ - pseudomártyr - psyoo-dom-ar'-toor/5575\">G5575</a>, <a href=\"#/G5576 - ψευδομαρτυρέω - pseudomartyréō - psyoo-dom-ar-too-reh'-o/5576\">G5576</a>, <a href=\"#/G5577 - ψευδομαρτυρία - pseudomartyría - psyoo-dom-ar-too-ree'-ah/5577\">G5577</a>"}]}